Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:03.38,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.38,0:00:05.77,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose, you'll become a pirate too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.65,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,This is an offer you can't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:10.88,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:11.90,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,And Miss Mai too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:13.15,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,EM, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:18.53,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It's a showdown! I'm gonna beat you, \Nthen save Princess Emi and Princess Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:24.54,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,This sorcerer lying dormant in the abyss has \Nobtained an even more accursed power!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:31.76,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The power to end the life of all beings \Non the face of this Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:36.94,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Prison Hades Emperor, Cocytus "Reverse"!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:39.31,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Break ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:40.93,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Superior call!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:44.69,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates who have died once, be resurrected!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:48.80,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,This is the true value of a Granblue deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.80,0:00:52.28,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,And its name is... \NEternal Resurrection Final Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:55.53,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Pirates can keep comin' back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.01,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it? Where'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:46.63,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:49.02,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll get Miss Emi back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:53.16,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You won't win against me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:56.03,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Not when I'm Reversed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:03:01.03,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui's Fist
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:14.71,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Grovel before the power of Cocytus "Reverse,"\N which I gained through that break ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:21.69,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Cocytus "Reverse" attacks your Vanguard, \Nwith a boost from Samurai Spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.85,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:31.10,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Drive trigger check.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.11,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Second check.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.26,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Critical trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:40.49,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I give all of the effects to Corrupt Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:56.13,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Without a perfect guard, \NI would've been in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:59.13,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Solar Falcon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.88,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not through yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:06.72,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Like waves, they come roaring to \Nshore, then pull you out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:08.72,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That's the terror of pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:12.04,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Ruin Shade attacks Hatred Chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:15.40,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Ruin Shade's skill. +2000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:25.07,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,His rear-guard was vaporized.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:27.50,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have any rear-guard \Nunits that can intercept.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.03,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,CI, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:32.29,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,And what's waiting for \Nhim in the third attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:37.61,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Corrupt Dragon, powered up with \Na critical trigger, Brazil!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:39.54,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you know where my deck is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:41.55,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Look for it, Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.09,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:47.05,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Become scraps of seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:52.81,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Corrupt Dragon attacks with a \Nboost from Sea Strolling Banshee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.81,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:56.31,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.47,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:11.83,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Unlock Dancing Cutlass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:17.55,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Two perfect guards?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:20.09,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky twerp!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.17,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.08,0:05:25.09,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Guys who don't give up attract luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:30.35,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, you're out of luck now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:35.07,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You got one card in your \Nhand left, while I got five.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:38.10,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,My advantage ain't goin' anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:44.36,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:48.31,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make you remember, Gouki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:49.37,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:52.42,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Stand and draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:59.75,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Desert Gator moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:01.30,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:07.05,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I call a pair of Brainy Papios!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:17.99,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Brainy Papio attacks your Vanguard \Nwith a boost from Desert Gator!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:20.02,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,No guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:22.59,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Damage trigger check!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.59,0:06:23.66,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:30.87,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,5 damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.16,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,5 D, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:34.16,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:37.41,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Brainy Papio's Counterblast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:40.67,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The malignant soul of a beast never sleeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:42.92,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I stand Desert Gator!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:49.93,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Brainy Papio attacks your Vanguard \Nwith a boost from Riot Horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.80,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:06:59.31,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Gouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:04.28,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna open your eyes with this \Ndeck that I swore an oath on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:10.81,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Ethics Buster Extreme attacks your \NVanguard with a boost from Blank Marsh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:17.54,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:19.71,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Drive trigger check!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.33,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Stand trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.68,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I stand Brainy Papio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.70,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,+5000 power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:31.98,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Beasts awaken fellow beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.35,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Riot Horn's skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:41.85,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,When a unit in the same vertical \Nline stands, this guy stands too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:46.11,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,So you've filled your front \Nand back rows again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:48.11,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Second check.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:51.79,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Grade 1... Beast Deity!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:52.49,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:55.74,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The banquet of beasts ain't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:59.50,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Ethics Buster Extreme's Limit Break!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:04.00,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,When a grade 1 or higher Beast Deity \Nappears in the drive check,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:07.00,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,one rear-guard can stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:10.01,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Brainy Papio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.76,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,His four left and right rear-guards stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.27,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,GK! Go, Kamui the Great, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:24.65,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't just any fist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:29.78,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fist of friendship, from me to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:35.53,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Brainy Papio attacks your Vanguard \Nwith a boost from Desert Gator!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:41.79,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,No guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:45.29,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,This fist is gonna open your eyes! Gouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:02.11,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui won!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:13.07,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why did I lose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:17.82,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,During my training here, \NI've tried out various decks,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.58,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,but of them all, this one fits me the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.82,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'll swear this right in front of you, Gouki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.75,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that no matter what rough \Nwaves comes from here on in,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.85,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,this deck and I will ride 'em out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.59,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna part with it lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:36.09,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:38.34,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Gouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:43.35,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Gouki, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:46.09,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui the Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:47.10,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,AYO?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:56.86,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Your fist did the trick, Kamui!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:06.13,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Cool, Kamui the Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:09.12,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,TMF! That's a man's friendship, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.69,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:12.38,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:15.63,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Rekka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:21.54,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he lost, why do I feel so moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:25.47,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, Brazil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:30.65,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You want something, Brazil?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.83,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Rekka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:39.28,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:51.44,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Gouki, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:54.54,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:58.70,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,We came to the school with \NNagisa to check it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:01.75,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,...and the next thing I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:04.43,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You were Reversed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:11.19,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,What's goin' on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:13.73,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.61,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Nagisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:18.07,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:20.32,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:21.45,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.84,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,...Rekka from Ultra-rare?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.54,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me she's also...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.04,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.95,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back Miss Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:35.04,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'm goin' too! They may \Nhave taken Nagisa also!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:46.56,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:52.31,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui, I'm not letting you get past me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:10.38,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting the same vibe that \NI did with you before, Gouki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:13.16,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:16.28,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa... has been Reversed too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:19.24,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Kamui!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:22.45,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,All it took was one look \Nfor you to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:25.96,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my future husband for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:30.99,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember promisin' \Nyou anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:34.36,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute when you're embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:38.55,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Even Reversed, she still doesn't \Nlisten to what a guy says!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:41.28,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa... Why are you wearing that makeup?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:46.18,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,My sweet, pure little sister is cuter \Nthan cute without any makeup...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:48.37,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking to Kamui right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:55.50,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Kamui? \NI've changed, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.51,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Changed how?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:13:00.50,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! You don't notice when \Na girl's become a woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:04.15,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, I was a fourth-grader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:08.18,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I met you, I wanted to \Ncommunicate my feelings right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:11.68,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I really was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:15.48,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,But now I'm in fifth grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:19.05,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, I've become a \Nlady who's a perfect fit for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.29,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tellin' ya, you \Nhaven't changed one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:23.73,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,And in the first place, \Nyou're only a year older!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:27.17,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,One year for a woman equals \Nthree years for a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.63,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, even though you're \Na first-year middle school student,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:34.12,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'm older than you emotionally!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:36.79,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,"A woman who's older than her \Nhusband," as people say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:39.92,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I didn't know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:42.51,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Ms. Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:47.47,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that older women \Nmake men successful, Brazil!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:49.45,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:52.60,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'll spell it out for you! \NI'm in love with...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.52,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.06,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,No! With Miss Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:13:59.31,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Bra...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:04.48,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-ah-ah, I'm not falling for that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:06.40,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I know all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:11.07,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That is, the tendency of men to eye other \Nwomen even when they have no feelings for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:15.55,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,But, you know, Kamui,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:18.21,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,your time to dream is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:22.21,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to return to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:26.21,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse! Forget it! No, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:30.47,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:37.11,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open your eyes with a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:43.80,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,No two ways about it, she's been Reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:48.11,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to bring her back to normal \Nis beating her in a fight, like with Gouki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:49.46,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:56.62,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:58.00,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:04.38,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I have to hurry up and save Miss Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:09.46,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't let Nagisa stay like this either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:13.47,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I must make my way to \Nthe imprisoned princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:19.77,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,But will I be able to leave behind \Nthis enchanted forest fairy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.61,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do, brave Kamui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:29.62,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Brave Kamui, will you choose Princess Emi? \NOr the emotionally older Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:31.11,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Brazil?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:36.27,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:38.82,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That choice is out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:41.25,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,We'll ask you one more time, Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:46.28,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Do you choose Princess Emi? \NOr the emotionally older Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:47.75,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Brazil?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:50.82,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:52.01,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:58.93,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Enhancement\NPeriod
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.89,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask you once more, Brazil!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:58.93,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Do you choose Princess Emi? \NOr the emotionally older Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.52,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,There ain't no end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:06.52,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Is fighting Nagisa the only thing I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:08.40,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:10.65,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Gouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:15.41,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for an older brother \Nto make his sister see the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.23,0:16:18.34,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'll count on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:22.91,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible, big bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:28.43,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It's bad enough you're not cheering \Nme on, but for you to betray me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:30.42,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,your own little sister, \Nand take Kamui's side...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:35.05,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Big bro, do you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:39.18,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.16,0:16:43.00,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Oy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:45.41,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I can't win against those tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:48.21,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kamui.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:48.61,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Gouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:49.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:53.36,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll even become an ogre if it's \Nfor the sake of Nagisa's happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:53.36,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kamui the Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:55.69,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,No interference!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:57.37,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Brazil...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:17:00.15,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're gonna fight, Kamui!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:03.87,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,And when I win, I'll make \Nyou forget all other women.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.34,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.34,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Brazil!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:19.10,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:21.28,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:26.71,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, boy-degozaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:27.60,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:31.11,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,...Ninja Master M?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:35.11,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That mask, that costume... There's no doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:38.66,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The guy that was successful at \Nthe Card Capital shop tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:42.14,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,then retired after passing the name \N"Ninja" on to the next generation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:44.12,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,LF, a legendary fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:47.25,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Master M, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:51.70,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I am not Ninja Master M.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:53.17,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this-degozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:18:02.07,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ninja Master Neo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:02.93,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Master
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:09.65,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Master Neo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.90,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Only the name's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:14.40,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,ONC, yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.96,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, thanks for helpin' me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:21.65,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,But what are you doing \Nhere, Ninja Master Neo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:24.13,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was here for the open house...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:26.66,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I can say no more-degozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:29.30,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've heard that voice before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.67,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That's not important now-degozaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.60,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I know what's going on-degozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:38.17,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me and go \Non ahead, boy-degozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.49,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't leave Nagisa like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:43.43,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Have faith in me-degozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:49.21,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that I'll bring her back to \Nnormal in your stead, boy-degozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:55.82,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, saving Lady Nagisa is \Nimportant, as is saving Lady Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:58.26,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,However, you are only one, Lord Kamui.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:01.62,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You can't save both at \Nthe same time-degozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:05.08,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:08.47,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to save them both
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:14.21,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,is for you to fight the one who \Ncaused this calamity and beat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:16.46,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The one who caused it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:22.88,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you cut it off at the roots, \Nthis disaster won't be contained.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:29.48,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Protect everyone you hold dear, boy-degozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:38.07,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Then you take care of Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.16,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui the Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:40.58,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:45.83,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I am your opponent-degozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:50.35,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You're just intent on interfering, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:56.46,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I need to show you \Njust how strong my love is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.84,0:20:01.33,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Love-degozaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:03.76,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,It's a beautiful word-degozaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.18,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Love me too-degozaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:08.47,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Now then! You're stuck with me-degozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.23,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:20.39,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The martial arts training hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:21.99,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Brazil?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:26.99,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning we're going to \Nsettle things here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:31.12,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't let you get one point of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:35.88,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Ninpo! Tatami mat flip!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:44.68,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,This won't do for a fight table-degozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:48.18,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! I don't need anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:52.56,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.28,0:20:55.21,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:57.62,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to your old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:00.19,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Big bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:07.57,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:13.08,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:15.47,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:20.59,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You lash out at your brother like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:24.64,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,My cute little sister, who I \Nbrought up with my own hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:27.19,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,says such a cruel thing to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:28.43,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:29.88,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Despair!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:32.85,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The end of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:38.10,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,The power of Reverse is \Nfearsome indeed... degozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:50.62,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sword
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:45.43,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I've always thought that Nagisa \Nwas much manlier than Gouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:48.14,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Brazil!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:50.62,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Owww...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:55.04,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi... Kaoru... You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.82,0:22:01.04,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Old man ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:03.05,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:08.18,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to teach you what happens \Nwhen you get in the way of my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.71,0:22:12.93,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,And thus a ninja's duty \Nis accomplished-degozaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:19.73,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.60,0:23:58.33,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Nagisa! Even you've been Reversed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:00.20,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:06.31,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens to the world, my eternal, \Nindestructible love for Kamui will stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.31,0:24:10.81,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Master Neo! Please take care of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.81,0:24:12.63,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Kamui!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.63,0:24:17.14,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,During the uproar in the middle school \Ndivision, we were still on the bus heading home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.46,0:24:19.52,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Ninja Master Returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.06,0:24:24.94,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Master Returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.52,0:24:22.44,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,Old man ninja who got in \Nthe way of a maiden's love?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.44,0:24:24.34,Main Dialog,Spoken,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to pay!